                        <h2 class="style-guide-title">Heading with Heading Description</h2>

                        <div class="heading__wrapper">
                            <h2 class="heading h1 highlight">@planetbeautyofficial</h2>
                            <p class="heading__description">Makeup, skincare, haircare, and more!</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <br><br>

                        <h2 class="style-guide-title">Class to hide elements</h2>
                        
                        <p>Classes available: <code class="code__inline">hidden__mobile</code> , <code class="code__inline">hidden__tablet</code> , <code class="code__inline">hidden__desktop</code>.</p>

                        <p>Reize the screen to see the other elements.</p>

                        <div class="hidden__tablet hidden__desktop">
                            <img  src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300/FAEAEA?text=Mobile" alt="test"/>
                            <code class="code__inline">hidden__tablet hidden__desktop</code>
                        </div>

                        <div class="hidden__mobile hidden__desktop">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300/FAEAEA?text=Tablet" alt="test"/>
                            <code>hidden__mobile hidden__desktop</code>
                        </div>

                        <div class="hidden__mobile hidden__tablet">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500x300/FAEAEA?text=Desktop" alt="test"/>
                            <code>hidden__mobile hidden__tablet</code>
                        </div>
                        
                        <br><br>

